      <guid isPermaLink="false">8c8c82605180657d98be8e63259a9cc5ee2710d9</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Jun 2025 07:38:30 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671b5d8736e5e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/671b5ebd17345.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Base game compatible!&lt;br&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Untested - please report any issues!!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;No, it's still not compatible with Welcome Luxury, that's not how code mods work.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Patches for NA and EU New Leaf, with yes and no petals&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Expanded Readme&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;NA WELCOME AMIIBO AND EU WELCOME AMIIBO ONLY. NOT COMPATIBLE WITH WELCOME LUXURY.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a code patch created for the user &lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/3341506" data-id="member_3341506"&gt;iloveanimalcrossing&lt;/a&gt;, who requested year-round cherry blossom trees. This patch was made with &lt;a href="https://github.com/Slattz/ACNL_REditor/releases" class="SelectedElement" target="_blank"&gt;ACNL REditor&lt;/a&gt;. Various additional versions were requested by &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/3909516"&gt;anqelicdoll.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Four versions and two flavors are available - you first pick your region (NA or EU) and which version you are running - the base game, Animal Crossing New Leaf, or the Welcome amiibo version. Then pick whether or not you want falling cherry blossom petals in the sky. Falling petals can cause lag, and are not recommended for emulator use. Nothing else has been changed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;More detailed installation instructions are included with the download.&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/cherryblossom_1577b.zip" type="application/zip"/>
