d,&amp;nbsp; they'll no longer have those changes, Since the file included in this mod only edits Sunny's name / Sunny's photo item name.&lt;br&gt;If you wouldnt like this to happen, just edit her name in the file you already have in the scripts folder manually using a hex editor by following this tutorial:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="SelectedElement"&gt;https://juette.tumblr.com/post/716504689334681600/a-comprehensive-guide-to-custom-villagers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Since Sunny's name is smaller than Wart jr's youll have to replace any remaining characters of wart jr's. name with the "dot" symbol in the hex editor to fill in the gaps and not cause glitches in the text.</description>
